    <h3 style="margin-top: 0">About these specimen(s)</h3>
    <p>This Prime is the very calculator that started my collection.</p>
    <p>Yes, I did have others before it - namely the TI-84+CE and the TI-Nspire CX II CAS - but those are eather boring
        calculators.</p>
    <p>The Prime is so different and so much more powerful that it inspired me to start collecting.</p>
    <p>And that's how we end up here.</p>
